%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF5.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF5&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF6.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF6&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF7.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF7&MI_00
