%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF5.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF5&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF6.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF6&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF7.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF7&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF8.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF8&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF9.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFF9&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFFA.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFFA&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFFB.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFFB&MI_00
%USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFFC.DeviceDesc%=VWUSBCam.Dev, USB\VID_2F0D&PID_FFFC&MI_00
